  <div id="block-block-119" class="block block-block first region-odd odd region-count-1 count-1">
      <h2 class="title">Curate this debate</h2>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>If you are an academic or highly knowledgeable about a particular debate could you give an hour or two a month to curate a debate?  </p><p>
<p> <a href="/node/24756?debate_url=http://idebate.org/debatabase/debates/health/house-would-legalize-sale-human-organs">Find out more </a></p>  </div>

  </div><!-- /.block -->

    <div id="block-block-118" class="block block-block last region-even even region-count-2 count-2">
      <h2 class="title">Be a debatabase editor</h2>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Idebate needs editors from around the world to check, moderate and create content for debatabase and the site more generally. Editors are vital in making the site run smoothly and ensuring that debates are as informative as possible.  </p><p>
<p> 
<a href="/node/24754?debate_url=http://idebate.org/debatabase/debates/health/house-would-legalize-sale-human-organs">Find out more  </a></p>  </div>

